def preprocess(tweet):
    result = re.sub(r'(RT\s@[A-Za-z]+[A-Za-z0-9-_]+)', '', tweet)

    result = re.sub(r'bit.ly/\S+', '', result)

    result = re.sub(r'#', ' ', result)
    result = re.sub(r'[^\w\s]', r'', result)

    result = re.sub(r'(\A\s+|\s+\Z)', '', result)
    result = tokenize(result)
